Patch 4 for version 7.3 - 14 January 2022

Changes
=======
1) Remove unused HD44780/U labels in translation class
2) Correct error when loading new playlist
3) Correct incorrect mute display when restoring volume with an external mpd client
4) Display Wi-Fi power management mode in display_wifi.sh
5) Correct shutdown failure when menu button held in
6) Add mpc version display to display_config.sh
7) Correct _spotify_ and _airplay_ source names to display as 'Spotify' and 'Airplay'
8) Correct Airplay settings in configuration class.py

To install the patch
====================
cd /usr/share/radio
wget http://www.bobrathbone.com/raspberrypi/packages/radiod-patch-7.3-4.tar.gz
tar -xvf radiod-patch-7.3-4.tar.gz
sudo systemctl restart radiod.service

This patch contains all previous patches unless patch 1

